latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy Birthday Sister! ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Late birthday post because we were so busy making memories ❤️ I love you so much! These 20 years and many more with you are priceless...I don’t think I can ever connect with anybody in this world the way we connect. Anytime I needed you, you were just there. I honestly can’t imagine a day when I don’t come to you and cry about stupidest things 😂😂 and you still console me...thank you for being my partner in crime. ❤️❤️ To many more crazy gossips, fights, laughter, and saving each other always! ❤️ mostly importantly I’ve always got your back sisterrrr! YOU ARE YOU! 😂😂❤️ HAPPIEST 23rd! 🥂🥂 @yashna._.thapar

What building a nail empire really looks like 💅✨
It’s not just polish and pretty nails—

It’s been 6 long years of ups and downs. Starting at 19 I’ve failed at things I’ve gotten better at some and it’s been a journey ♥️ 

It’s sourcing, designing, teaching, mentoring, marketing, and showing up every single day.

From the salon floor to product launches, this is the behind-the-scenes of passion turned into power.
It started with the love of nails and it’s turned into a reality of building a nail empire ♥️

This table had been on my wishlist forever, just waiting for the perfect corner to let it shine — and I finally found it. It’s sculptural, grounding, and effortlessly elevates the space alongside my bold Maximilian sofa. A true statement without shouting.

Sometimes, all it takes is one perfect piece to complete the story.
